{"tid":2126082,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多位曾經喜愛POKEMON既90後聽返歷代BGM有無特別感嘆?","createTime":"2020-07-26T15:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T06:37:14.000Z","uid":86628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"864f7828d54dd9bba3b9cd853fdb814a834f8646","tid":2126082,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1jasjOhy7Zc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1jasjOhy7Zc&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=93a49f4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1jasjOhy7Zc</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我已經老啦 POKEMON亦都有廿年歷史<br />\n以前歡樂無憂玩遊戲既日子以經過去<br />\n人愈大 愈多煩惱 愈多負擔 愈少時間<br />\n細個只需要返學放學玩遊戲 同朋友玩<br />\n以前最鐘意玩就係POKEMON, GBC GBA NDS 模擬器 改版 漆金綠寶石 上到大學都仲有玩<br />\n但到出黎做野真係太忙 無時間再玩 就算玩返亦都唔係果隻滋味 成日驚住仲有其他野做<br />\n無曬私人時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時做野都會開返BGM黎聽返回憶下<br />\n真係百般滋味在心頭<br />\n自己住既地方變到唔到曬 香港唔再係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心境愈都唔再係以前咁單純 唉..."},{"pid":"d98a75f81590a0e77b0ab1c0455310ae2d14287a","tid":2126082,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"而家只能盼望日後仲有時間可以玩多D POKEMON既遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dbfa74037786d83f73ef09feebdddcda5eddcd","tid":2126082,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/